                           <desc>List of witnesses for the land ownership in <placeName ref="LOC7345MekuatMaret">Mǝkʷǝʿāt Maret</placeName>.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              ኆልቈ፡ ምስክር፡ ዘምኵዓት። ተክለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወድ፡ በዓተይ፡ ሹም፡ ተክለ፡ ኢየሱስ። ...</q>
                           
                           <note> It lists witnesses involved in a dispute over land ownership (s.
                              <ref target="#a4" type="item">Additio 4</ref>). The <persName ref="PRS13068KirosMKL" role="scribe">scribe Kiros</persName> mentions himself at the end of the note.
                           </note>
                        </item>
