                           <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="LIT3058RepCh338">ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee...”</title> is written in an early hand on the inserted folium <locus from="10ra" to="10va">10ra-va</locus>, 
                              probably from an earlier manuscript (same as <locus target="#11"/>?)</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>

                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
